    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a significant project or a parts donor. The engine is functional but suffers from multiple fluid leaks and a persistent rough idle, while the transmission exhibits harsh shifting between gears. On the exterior, the paint is heavily oxidized with several areas of surface rust and a noticeable dent in the rear quarter panel. The interior shows substantial wear, including torn upholstery and a headliner that is beginning to sag. This car is sold as-is and will require a fair amount of work to be roadworthy again.",
