      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car, and honestly, it's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily errands and weekend trips. I've taken great care of it, and it still looks and runs beautifully! If you're looking for a dependable ride that's ready to hit the road today, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
      "price": 28900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This driver-focused icon features a high-revving 3.2L DOHC inline-six powerplant equipped with individual throttle bodies and advanced variable valve timing for razor-sharp throttle response. Power is managed through a tactile six-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power delivery through the corners. The chassis remains composed with excellent torsional rigidity and a suspension geometry tuned for communicative feedback. While displaying the honest patina of an enjoyed machine, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering a visceral, analog experience for the discerning pilot.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Used car for sale. Good condition. Runs well. Clean interior. Recent service completed. Title in hand.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between reliability and premium feel. The exterior paint retains a beautiful depth and gloss, though light stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper reflect its honest history as a dependable driver. Step inside to an exceptionally clean cabin where the leather seats remain soft and supportive, showing only minor creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All onboard electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts with precision, backed by a complete service record and a recent professional inspection. The tires are recent additions with deep tread, and the brakes feel crisp and responsive. This car has been smoke-free, garage-kept, and treated with the respect it deserves. It is a turn-key opportunity for anyone seeking a high-quality vehicle without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
