      "description": "This vehicle represents a premier acquisition for the professional seeking a synthesis of reliability and executive presence. Maintained to a rigorous standard, it exhibits the mechanical integrity and aesthetic poise expected of a high-caliber pre-owned asset. Our commitment to excellence ensures this vehicle is prepared for immediate service, offering a distinguished alternative to new inventory. We invite you to experience a vehicle that balances proven performance with exceptional value, presented in a condition that reflects diligent stewardship.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
